HTMLParserCommon
public abstract class ContainerParser<C extends Container,IC extends InfoCollector<C>,ES extends ecologylab.xml.ElementState>
extends DocumentParser<C,IC,ES>

DocumentParser base class for all Container documents, that is, those in which the resulting Document will be of type Container, with all of its concomitant local collections et al.

References contains fields for search, in case those will be useful.

Author:
andruid
